  "title": "Somebody Will Go on a Date During This Show",
  "description": "From the team that legally married two improvisers last year, now it is your turn to get in on the action! Join our team as a member of the audience goes on a BLIND DATE with one of our improvisers, inspiring the entirety of our improvised performance. Maybe you'll even find a love that makes you say yes, and...",
  "credits": "<strong>Director</strong>: Grace Fitzgerald<br/>",
  "website": "https://www.instagram.com/scatterbrainimprov",
  "plain_language": "\"Somebody Will Go on a Date During This Show\" is an improvised show. At the beginning, an audience member is selected to go on a blind date with one of the improvisers. Their date will inspire the show. The show is improvised, and made up live. It is comedic. At the end, the two people on the date will reveal if they are willing to go on a second one.",
